creator: Siscomplay
descriptionHtml:
This application allows you to play padel, providing you with an infinite number of features such as chat, notifications, reminders, comparatives, historical, statistics or graphs of your level evolution among others.

Now, you can organize your own league with your friends.

Operational functionalities:
- View and sign up for matches in progress.
- Create, edit, cancel matches.
- Read the messages of the league (private and public).
- Record the results of matches
- View statistics of the ranking of levels and classification.
- Manage favorite players
- Manage the user profile.
- See list of players
- See the information of the clubs in each league.
- Compare the results of 2 players
- Manage reminders.
- Receive notifications of new open matches, substitutions, full matches, messages, etc.
- Silence and / or deactivate notifications according to preferences (1 day, 3 days or a week)
- Configure parameters to receive notifications: by level, sex, province, time, days of the week, etc.
descriptionShort: Complete platform to organize a league and play your paddle matches.

title: Rádical Padel

creator: Siscomplay
descriptionHtml:
If you have a CLUB, Rádical allows you to effortlessly organize your own paddle league in a completely self-managed way by the participants themselves.

Now, it also includes a powerful FREE module for clubs, for managing online paddle court reservations.

As a player, you have countless features such as chat, notices, reminders, comparative, historical, statistics and graphs of your level evolution, among others, in addition to climbing in the level ranking and classification.

Developed with the contribution and recommendations of more than 20,000 players, with more than 350,000 organized matches, Radical Padel is, simply, the best APP for padel matches organizing.

OPTIONS YOU HAVE AS A PLAYER
- Statistics and level evolution graphs
- Online court reservations
- Sign up for matches in progress
- Record results
- Receive Notices of new matches
- Request to be replaced
- Message chat
- Manage favorite players
- Set your reminders
- Manage your schedule
- See comparisons between players
- Climb in the classification and in the level ranking
- Choose light or dark interface
- And a multitude of fully customized smart options like availability, favorite player filter, historical, etc.

OPTIONS YOU HAVE AS A CLUB
- You will have a powerful FREE online booking APP
- Direct access from your App session.
- Indicate the schedule of each court and the duration of the matches.
- Define user groups, with prices according to the group.
- Define the maximum advance with which you can reserve.
- Define minimum advance notice with which you can cancel.
- Allow payment by card, at reception or with purse.
- Allow full or proportional track payouts (each player their share)
- Allow to select track or assign it directly.
- Block tracks, dates and times.
- Reserve recurring or repeating tracks (fixed tracks)
- Publish matches for players to sign up.
- Open matches for paddle or school classes.
- Modify or correct matches.
- View occupation statistics by dates, time slots, etc.
descriptionShort: Complete platform to organize a league and play your paddle matches.

title: Rádical Padel

creator: Siscomplay
descriptionHtml:
If you have a CLUB, we provide a reservation app designed to increase activity in your club, featuring a powerful free reservation module that includes everything you need to manage your club efficiently.

If you are a PLAYER, we offer you an app that will excite you—friendly, motivating, with an effective level calculation algorithm, and a comprehensive push notification system for all important actions.

Developed with input and suggestions from over 50,000 players, with more than 1 million matches organized:

- No Commission Reservations: Manage court bookings efficiently and without additional costs.
- Push Notifications: Stay informed about your reservations, matches, statistics, and all important actions.
- Intuitive Interface: Compatible with Android and iPhone devices, offering a friendly and easy-to-use interface for both administrators and players.
- Matches: Engaging match organization system with statistics and an effective level calculation algorithm.

Benefits for Clubs:

- Increased Activity: Generate more reservations and competitions, leading to higher revenue and greater member loyalty.
- Intelligent Monetization Model: Pay only for the players who sign up for competitions organized through the app, maximizing your return on investment.
- Immediate Integration: Quick and easy setup to start benefiting your club immediately. Additionally, we offer ongoing support for any needs.
- Customized Environment: Create a personalized testing environment with your club's image to demonstrate the advantages to your members.
descriptionShort: Much more than a reservation app.
